BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Tickets $25\nPurchase Tickets\nNew-York based guitarist and composer shares new work commissioned by Roulette.\n\nRoulette Commissioned Artist Chuck Roth shares new material.\nRoth\nis a New-York based guitarist and composer. Both his songwriting and improvised music practice allow him to explore the guitar’s range of sounds and the way musical forms evolve over time. He is interested in exploring the vast palette of sounds and textures available on the guitar without effects\, objects or pedals.\nA livestream will be available free of charge at 8pm on the day of the performance and archived for future viewing.
DURATION:PT2H
LOCATION:Roulette Intermedium\, 509 Atlantic Ave\, Brooklyn\, NY
